# Bayesian modelling 

## (Super) silly example: drug

.pull-left[
**Existing knowledge**
- Population registries
- Observational studies
- Small/pilot RCTs
- Expert opinion
]
.pull-right[
.alignright[
**Current data**
- Large(r) scale RCT
